description: ​Hotel Shri Gokul Anand, located in Dahisar East, Mumbai, offers 30 well-appointed rooms—including standard, deluxe, and executive categories—with modern amenities such as air conditioning, LED TVs, tea/coffee makers, and complimentary Wi-Fi. Conveniently situated near Dahisar Railway Station and Sanjay Gandhi National Park, it caters to both business and leisure travelers. Additional facilities include a banquet hall and a terrace garden for events and gatherings. ​
